room_title: Escape room "Taken" by Fort Wayne Escape Room in Fort Wayne
room_address: 327 E Wayne St #200 Fort Wayne, IN 46802
room_description:
You have been taken! Now you are being held prisoner in an unknown location, with no means of communicating with the outside world.
But luckily, you just so happen to have a very particular set of skills! Skills that make you a nightmare for any kidnapper, terrorist, and/or general bad guy.
You will have to rely on your ingenuity, resourcefulness, and creativity to make your daring escape before your captors return!
